00:16:12,320 --> 00:16:13,880
are too far apart.

575
00:16:13,880 --> 00:16:14,880
Let's move them closer.

576
00:16:14,880 --> 00:16:16,120
Yeah, I agree.

577
00:16:16,120 --> 00:16:17,360
Let's put all

578
00:16:17,360 --> 00:16:18,880
five plates in a row.

579
00:16:18,880 --> 00:16:19,240
Okay?

580
00:16:19,240 --> 00:16:19,720
Yeah.

581
00:16:19,720 --> 00:16:20,360
All five in a row.

582
00:16:20,360 --> 00:16:20,960
That works.

583
00:16:21,160 --> 00:16:22,640
Then I definitely can't

584
00:16:22,640 --> 00:16:23,760
reach the far one.

585
00:16:23,820 --> 00:16:25,360
(The "border zone")

586
00:16:25,360 --> 00:16:26,400
We can figure it out.

587
00:16:26,400 --> 00:16:27,760
Let's just close our eyes like this.

588
00:16:27,760 --> 00:16:28,240
Okay?

589
00:16:28,240 --> 00:16:30,080
And you two can't reach either, right?

590
00:16:30,080 --> 00:16:30,920
For example,

591
00:16:30,920 --> 00:16:32,280
if I stand up, I have to walk back.

592
00:16:33,400 --> 00:16:34,400
Right, he'd need to take a step.

593
00:16:34,800 --> 00:16:35,720
So let's just do it like this.

594
00:16:36,720 --> 00:16:37,400
Like this.

595
00:16:37,400 --> 00:16:38,360
Okay.

596
00:16:38,360 --> 00:16:38,800
Okay, deal.

597
00:16:39,240 --> 00:16:40,400
Let's start.

598
00:16:40,400 --> 00:16:41,360
Let's draw identities first.

599
00:16:41,360 --> 00:16:43,990
(Drawing identities)

600
00:16:44,000 --> 00:16:45,480
I'll just hang this here.

601
00:16:45,480 --> 00:16:46,600
Anyone can reach it.

602
00:16:46,600 --> 00:16:47,400
(Glutton Ghost selector stick)

603
00:16:47,400 --> 00:16:48,680
Really? Can Ding reach it?

604
00:16:48,680 --> 00:16:50,240
What if he's the Glutton Ghost
and needs to pick at the end?

605
00:16:50,240 --> 00:16:51,280
He actually can't reach it.

606
00:16:51,280 --> 00:16:51,800
He can step out.

607
00:16:51,800 --> 00:16:52,760
I can step out.

608
00:16:52,760 --> 00:16:53,440
It's fine.

609
00:16:53,760 --> 00:16:55,480
I'll send
your Glutton Ghost identity to you.

610
00:16:57,160 --> 00:16:58,080
Okay, check it.

611
00:17:02,800 --> 00:17:03,520
We draw numbers.

612
00:17:05,200 --> 00:17:05,920
This is too close.

613
00:17:05,920 --> 00:17:06,400
Honestly,

614
00:17:06,400 --> 00:17:08,110
if I eat something, you'll all hear it.

615
00:17:08,310 --> 00:17:10,000
Why are you worried about that?

616
00:17:10,440 --> 00:17:11,560
(Instant suspicion activated)
Are you the one eating?

617
00:17:11,560 --> 00:17:12,350
You're so nervous.

618
00:17:13,000 --> 00:17:13,680
Yeah, it's me eating.

619
00:17:13,680 --> 00:17:14,560
Right, it's me.

620
00:17:14,560 --> 00:17:15,680
Vote for me if you dare.

621
00:17:16,110 --> 00:17:16,920
Vote for him.

622
00:17:16,920 --> 00:17:17,590
I'm done with this round.

623
00:17:17,590 --> 00:17:18,540
(Ding becomes top suspect)

624
00:17:18,640 --> 00:17:19,200
Flip it over.

625
00:17:20,110 --> 00:17:21,880
(Suspicious)
You're really targeting him.

626
00:17:21,880 --> 00:17:22,560
I'm not.

627
00:17:24,560 --> 00:17:25,040
Come on.

628
00:17:25,800 --> 00:17:26,830
Night falls. Eyes closed.

629
00:17:27,340 --> 00:17:29,780
(Glutton bug fix, round 1)

630
00:17:34,200 --> 00:17:35,280
Number one, open your eyes.

631
00:17:44,100 --> 00:17:45,460
(Blank role)

632
00:17:46,060 --> 00:17:47,380
(Right)

633
00:17:48,640 --> 00:17:50,440
Number one's taking so long.
Are they eating?

634
00:17:50,760 --> 00:17:53,240
Did the Glutton Ghost finish already?

635
00:17:53,240 --> 00:17:54,320
Honestly...

636
00:17:54,320 --> 00:17:55,380
(Blank confusion tactic)

637
00:17:56,000 --> 00:17:57,520
He's coughing from sourness.

638
00:17:57,520 --> 00:18:00,280
And I swear you can smell it.

639
00:18:01,400 --> 00:18:02,320
My nose is really sensitive.

640
00:18:04,720 --> 00:18:05,560
You can really smell it?

641
00:18:05,560 --> 00:18:06,120
Yeah.

642
00:18:06,120 --> 00:18:07,040
I already smell it.

643
00:18:07,040 --> 00:18:09,600
The lemon smell is
coming from Ding Chengxin's side.

644
00:18:09,840 --> 00:18:10,680
I swear I...

645
00:18:12,280 --> 00:18:13,480
Number one, close your eyes.

646
00:18:14,160 --> 00:18:15,160
Number two, open your eyes.

647
00:18:22,100 --> 00:18:28,300
(Glutton Ghost)

648
00:18:34,080 --> 00:18:35,040
Number two.

649
00:18:35,040 --> 00:18:38,300
(Glutton Ghost)

650
00:18:38,320 --> 00:18:39,040
I'm pretty good with sour food.

651
00:18:43,480 --> 00:18:45,440
Number two is definitely eating.

652
00:18:45,440 --> 00:18:46,440
I think so too.

653
00:18:46,440 --> 00:18:47,600
Yeah, I feel like someone's eating.

654
00:18:48,000 --> 00:18:49,400
How did I hear that?

655
00:18:50,160 --> 00:18:52,120
I'm sure number two is eating the lemon.

656
00:18:52,120 --> 00:18:53,160
Who is it? Why is no one talking?

657
00:18:53,160 --> 00:18:53,760
Someone's staying quiet.

658
00:18:53,760 --> 00:18:55,080
Why is someone not speaking?

659
00:18:55,080 --> 00:18:56,280
(The quiet one)

660
00:18:56,280 --> 00:18:57,760
(Suspicion redirected)
Someone's not talking.

661
00:18:58,320 --> 00:18:59,800
How are you so sure?

662
00:18:59,800 --> 00:19:02,360
Because I smell lemon.

663
00:19:03,060 --> 00:19:04,540
(Self-check mode)

664
00:19:04,720 --> 00:19:05,320
Really?

665
00:19:05,320 --> 00:19:06,200
You know

666
00:19:06,200 --> 00:19:07,440
when you bite into a lemon,

667
00:19:07,440 --> 00:19:09,520
it bursts juice

668
00:19:09,520 --> 00:19:10,800
into the air.

669
00:19:10,800 --> 00:19:11,680
Did it spray on your face?

670
00:19:13,880 --> 00:19:14,320
No.

671
00:19:14,920 --> 00:19:16,840
Next we should
smell everyone's breath one by one.

672
00:19:17,960 --> 00:19:19,080
That's not necessary.

673
00:19:19,520 --> 00:19:20,720
No way, that's disgusting.

674
00:19:20,720 --> 00:19:21,280
That's disgusting.

675
00:19:22,560 --> 00:19:23,320
Zhou Ke.

676
00:19:23,320 --> 00:19:24,200
Zhou Ke sounds like...

677
00:19:24,920 --> 00:19:25,480
Jin Jing.

678
00:19:25,480 --> 00:19:27,000
She's basically drooling while talking.

679
00:19:27,000 --> 00:19:27,480
Right.

680
00:19:27,480 --> 00:19:28,440
Me? Drooling?

681
00:19:28,440 --> 00:19:29,150
(I...)

682
00:19:29,150 --> 00:19:30,300
(I've been here)

683
00:19:30,300 --> 00:19:31,540
(the whole time…)

684
00:19:31,700 --> 00:19:32,840
(You're suspicious)

685
00:19:32,840 --> 00:19:33,880
Number two, close your eyes.

686
00:19:35,280 --> 00:19:36,320
Number three, open your eyes.

687
00:19:36,940 --> 00:19:38,780
(Slot three empty)

688
00:19:40,440 --> 00:19:41,080
Say something.

689
00:19:41,720 --> 00:19:42,440
Say something.

690
00:19:42,920 --> 00:19:44,120
Ding is completely silent.

691
00:19:44,520 --> 00:19:46,240
(Silence raises suspicion)
I've been here the whole time.

692
00:19:46,240 --> 00:19:47,040
Where's Ning?

693
00:19:47,640 --> 00:19:48,160
I'm

694
00:19:48,160 --> 00:19:48,760
here.

695
00:19:50,360 --> 00:19:51,280
What do you mean?

696
00:19:52,520 --> 00:19:54,000
Our rule is that everyone has

697
00:19:54,000 --> 00:19:55,440
to keep talking every night.

698
00:19:55,440 --> 00:19:55,800
Okay.

699
00:19:58,820 --> 00:20:00,220
(Causing chaos)

700
00:20:00,800 --> 00:20:01,840
And now Ding Chengxin

701
00:20:01,840 --> 00:20:03,400
can't even talk.

702
00:20:03,400 --> 00:20:04,680
(Zhou Keyu becomes the prime suspect)
Why can't I talk?

703
00:20:04,680 --> 00:20:05,480
He's overwhelmed.

704
00:20:05,480 --> 00:20:06,080
Why is the plate...

705
00:20:06,080 --> 00:20:06,880
The plate moved.

706
00:20:09,200 --> 00:20:10,640
Trying to create a distraction.

707
00:20:11,440 --> 00:20:12,680
Player No. 3, close your eyes.

708
00:20:13,280 --> 00:20:13,800
It's finished.

709
00:20:13,860 --> 00:20:15,940
(It's really gone)

710
00:20:15,960 --> 00:20:17,000
Player No. 4, open your eyes.

711
00:20:17,780 --> 00:20:19,580
(Seat No. 4 is empty)

712
00:20:19,960 --> 00:20:20,680
Player No. 4,

713
00:20:20,680 --> 00:20:22,080
are you out of lemons?

714
00:20:22,560 --> 00:20:23,480
Take a look at the table.

715
00:20:23,960 --> 00:20:25,400
I think it's one
of the players on either end.

716
00:20:25,400 --> 00:20:26,160
I think so too.

717
00:20:26,160 --> 00:20:27,400
(The spotlight falls on both ends)

718
00:20:27,400 --> 00:20:28,760
Seriously?

719
00:20:29,320 --> 00:20:31,800
Yeah. The players on both ends
are slurring their words.

720
00:20:31,800 --> 00:20:32,960
Very noticeably.

721
00:20:33,280 --> 00:20:33,760
What?

722
00:20:37,640 --> 00:20:39,280
What are you trying to say?

723
00:20:39,680 --> 00:20:42,160
You've been keeping quiet, Ding.
It feels too deliberate.

724
00:20:42,160 --> 00:20:42,520
Exactly.

725
00:20:42,520 --> 00:20:42,980
(Glutton Ghost begins
shifting the blame)

726
00:20:43,120 --> 00:20:44,320
He's just trying to stop us

727
00:20:44,320 --> 00:20:45,880
(Diversion works)
from smelling the lemon on his breath.

728
00:20:46,440 --> 00:20:47,240
Is that so?

729
00:20:48,040 --> 00:20:50,680
Well, then there's nothing we can do.

730
00:20:52,000 --> 00:20:53,000
Player No. 4, close your eyes.

731
00:20:53,640 --> 00:20:54,760
Player No. 5, open your eyes.

732
00:20:59,100 --> 00:21:00,300
(Both players on the ends
happen to be No. 5)

733
00:21:00,320 --> 00:21:01,400
Say something.

734
00:21:01,400 --> 00:21:01,840
Talk.

735
00:21:01,840 --> 00:21:02,240
Hello?

736
00:21:02,240 --> 00:21:02,920
Say something.

737
00:21:03,720 --> 00:21:04,400
Someone looked up.

738
00:21:09,480 --> 00:21:11,040
Who's staying silent?

739
00:21:11,040 --> 00:21:12,640
One person hasn't spoken at all.

740
00:21:15,180 --> 00:21:17,340
(Suspect identified)

741
00:21:21,860 --> 00:21:23,700
(Eyes locked on)

742
00:21:23,720 --> 00:21:24,520
Alright.

743
00:21:24,520 --> 00:21:26,000
The sourness got to them.

744
00:21:28,160 --> 00:21:29,160
Alright.

745
00:21:30,660 --> 00:21:33,580
(Drama begins)

746
00:21:33,760 --> 00:21:34,840
You've finished eating, right?

747
00:21:39,280 --> 00:21:41,320
He puts on a show every single night.

748
00:21:41,640 --> 00:21:43,000
Every night without fail.

749
00:21:43,000 --> 00:21:43,520
That's right.

750
00:21:43,520 --> 00:21:44,400
(Troublemaker)

751
00:21:44,400 --> 00:21:45,480
Player No. 5, close your eyes.

752
00:21:46,040 --> 00:21:47,280
Glutton Ghost, open your eyes.

753
00:21:50,160 --> 00:21:52,280
Glutton Ghost...

754
00:21:53,160 --> 00:21:55,040
The Glutton Ghost has arrived.

755
00:21:55,040 --> 00:21:57,320
Glutton Ghost, choose one player
to become your Helper Ghost.

756
00:21:57,680 --> 00:21:59,720
Let me think.

757
00:21:59,720 --> 00:22:01,720
Take your time.

758
00:22:02,560 --> 00:22:04,600
Who should I pick?

759
00:22:05,280 --> 00:22:06,240
Your voice is so irritating.

760
00:22:06,240 --> 00:22:06,800
You're next to me.

761
00:22:07,640 --> 00:22:08,480
Go wash up, then.

762
00:22:13,900 --> 00:22:16,140
(Helper Ghost)

763
00:22:16,160 --> 00:22:17,200
Alright.

764
00:22:17,720 --> 00:22:18,640
Have she made her choice?

765
00:22:21,480 --> 00:22:23,080
If you won't pick me as your teammate...

766
00:22:23,840 --> 00:22:25,240
Then I'll choose you instead.

767
00:22:25,680 --> 00:22:26,920
Feels like they picked someone

768
00:22:26,920 --> 00:22:28,000
sitting very close by.

769
00:22:29,760 --> 00:22:30,920
How can you tell?

770
00:22:31,180 --> 00:22:33,140
(Uncanny sixth sense)

771
00:22:33,480 --> 00:22:34,600
Daybreak. Everyone, open your eyes.

772
00:22:34,600 --> 00:22:44,380
(Glutton Ghost: Jin Jing.
Helper Ghost: Zhou Keyu)

773
00:22:45,840 --> 00:22:47,320
So the lemon was eaten over here, huh?

774
00:22:47,320 --> 00:22:50,860
(Glutton Ghost: Jin Jing.
Helper Ghost: Zhou Keyu.)

775
00:22:50,880 --> 00:22:51,920
Great.

776
00:22:52,440 --> 00:22:54,960
I don't even need to think it through.

777
00:22:54,960 --> 00:22:56,440
I've got a theory.

778
00:22:56,680 --> 00:22:57,440
I know who it is.

779
00:23:01,280 --> 00:23:03,640
What's the tissue for?

780
00:23:05,240 --> 00:23:06,560
I was sitting in the middle.

781
00:23:06,560 --> 00:23:08,120
I kept my eyes closed for so long

782
00:23:08,120 --> 00:23:09,120
so my makeup started smudging.

783
00:23:09,120 --> 00:23:11,000
Or was it because the lemon
was too sour?

784
00:23:11,440 --> 00:23:13,680
So we're going straight after me now?

785
00:23:13,880 --> 00:23:14,320
Fine.

786
00:23:14,320 --> 00:23:15,400
Then let me prove it.

787
00:23:15,400 --> 00:23:17,040
If you're confident,
have another piece.

788
00:23:17,040 --> 00:23:18,120
Let's see if you cry.

789
00:23:18,720 --> 00:23:19,120
What about

790
00:23:19,120 --> 00:23:20,560
we start over?

791
00:23:20,560 --> 00:23:21,280
I'm Player No. 5.

792
00:23:22,760 --> 00:23:23,440
I'm Player No. 5.

793
00:23:23,440 --> 00:23:24,880
(Reveals himself as Player No. 5)
That means the lemon had been eaten

794
00:23:24,880 --> 00:23:26,400
before Player No. 5's turn.

795
00:23:26,400 --> 00:23:28,040
And I have a witness.

796
00:23:29,100 --> 00:23:30,420
(Ding's witness)

797
00:23:30,760 --> 00:23:31,840
You two opened your eyes together?

798
00:23:32,240 --> 00:23:32,560
Yes.

799
00:23:35,120 --> 00:23:36,680
Yes, Ning and I can confirm each other.

800
00:23:36,680 --> 00:23:37,360
We woke up together.

801
00:23:37,880 --> 00:23:39,560
So the lemon had been eaten
before Player No. 5.

802
00:23:39,940 --> 00:23:41,940
(Scrambling to come up with a response)

803
00:23:42,040 --> 00:23:44,240
You're awfully eager to clear your name.

804
00:23:45,440 --> 00:23:47,200
He deliberately chose the last
No. 5 in the order.

805
00:23:47,720 --> 00:23:48,840
Me?

806
00:23:49,360 --> 00:23:50,560
The very last one.

807
00:23:50,560 --> 00:23:51,760
(Quickly agrees)
Trying to remove every bit of suspicion.

808
00:23:51,760 --> 00:23:53,440
How is that clearing myself completely?

809
00:23:54,280 --> 00:23:55,320
Doesn't that make the two of them

810
00:23:55,320 --> 00:23:56,640
(Strategy: Acting clueless about rules)
obviously innocent?

811
00:23:57,120 --> 00:23:58,640
It could also be the Glutton Ghost.

812
00:23:58,640 --> 00:23:59,480
Not necessarily.

813
00:23:59,480 --> 00:24:00,400
That's not how it works.

814
00:24:00,880 --> 00:24:01,320
Glutton Ghost.

815
00:24:01,320 --> 00:24:02,520
(Ding's primary suspect)
Your turn, Glutton Ghost.

816
00:24:02,800 --> 00:24:03,960
I'm Player No. 2.

817
00:24:05,580 --> 00:24:07,300
(No. 2)

818
00:24:07,520 --> 00:24:08,280
You're No. 2. Alright.

819
00:24:08,880 --> 00:24:10,520
When I opened my eyes,

820
00:24:10,520 --> 00:24:12,480
there were still lemons on the table.

821
00:24:12,480 --> 00:24:13,040
Alright.

822
00:24:13,700 --> 00:24:14,960
(This round is anything
but straightforward)

823
00:24:14,960 --> 00:24:16,080
So no one had eaten one yet?

824
00:24:16,080 --> 00:24:16,560
That's right.

825
00:24:16,560 --> 00:24:16,960
Really?

826
00:24:17,300 --> 00:24:18,340
(Mind goes completely blank)

827
00:24:18,520 --> 00:24:19,360
What number are you?

828
00:24:19,920 --> 00:24:20,360
Who?

829
00:24:20,360 --> 00:24:20,920
Me?

830
00:24:20,920 --> 00:24:21,200
Him.

831
00:24:22,480 --> 00:24:23,640
You're allowed to lie, aren't you?

832
00:24:24,040 --> 00:24:25,040
Yes.

833
00:24:25,040 --> 00:24:26,760
You could even say you're Player No. 1.

834
00:24:26,760 --> 00:24:28,040
I am Player No. 1.

835
00:24:28,040 --> 00:24:28,980
Why would I lie?

836
00:24:28,980 --> 00:24:30,860
(Is my intuition really that accurate?)

837
00:24:35,800 --> 00:24:38,640
I'm the real Player No. 1.

838
00:24:38,640 --> 00:24:39,320
Fine.

839
00:24:39,320 --> 00:24:41,720
That's right. I was the first
to open my eyes on the first night.

840
00:24:41,720 --> 00:24:44,040
I'm just an ordinary player.

841
00:24:46,820 --> 00:24:48,740
(Pokes)

842
00:24:49,160 --> 00:24:50,880
The first night
was completely uneventful.

843
00:24:50,880 --> 00:24:52,240
No one ate a lemon.

844
00:24:53,400 --> 00:24:56,760
And someone else woke up
on the same night as I did.

845
00:25:00,680 --> 00:25:02,680
I have someone
who opened their eyes with me.

846
00:25:02,680 --> 00:25:03,360
The first person I saw.

847
00:25:03,640 --> 00:25:05,440
You have someone like that too?

848
00:25:05,880 --> 00:25:06,120
Yes.

849
00:25:06,360 --> 00:25:07,000
I'm Player No. 5.

850
00:25:07,000 --> 00:25:07,680
I have a witness.

851
00:25:08,480 --> 00:25:09,720
I'm Player No. 2.

852
00:25:09,920 --> 00:25:11,360
On the first night,
He and I opened our eyes.

853
00:25:11,800 --> 00:25:13,320
We didn't see anyone eat a lemon.

854
00:25:13,320 --> 00:25:15,820
(Speechless)

855
00:25:15,820 --> 00:25:17,820
